{"tid":208411,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"黃金周立山黑部行程咁樣掂唔掂？","createTime":"2017-04-19T13:38:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-26T09:50:37.000Z","uid":31666,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"41db041bb38dfa22a690a1b7c94ce2067aeb41e3","tid":208411,"uid":31666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T13:38:18.000Z","msg":"Day 1  東京晨早搭新幹線去松本 上高地（河童橋、大正池、田化池）上高地住宿<br />\n<br />\nDay 2 上高地經信濃大町上立山 落山後去宇奈月溫泉住宿 <br />\n<br />\nDay 3 黑部峽谷鐵道 去金澤 金澤住宿<br />\n<br />\nDay 4 金澤去五箇山，白川鄉"},{"pid":"6b825e7ea11be8954cb28443c23277cd96efb390","tid":208411,"uid":31666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T13:39:09.000Z","msg":"屌，噤錯制未打完，自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fba119edc13b378574f41df8ae822ff7f7284a4","tid":208411,"uid":34692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T13:52:53.000Z","msg":"東京冇新幹線去松本， 一係坐新幹線去長野再搭落松本， 一係喺新宿直接坐特急去松本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上高地中午之前景色比較好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />， 巴打會唔會考慮轉一轉行程<br />\n另外會唔會落返松本住一晚 第二日直接去立山黑部好啲 因為如果係上高地出發又係會好趕 除非你朝早五六點就出門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ab8e0e823856d91074b44b316fe17fec7365742","tid":208411,"uid":31666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T14:01:05.000Z","msg":"4月29至 5月3<br />\n<br />\nDay 1 東京晨早搭新幹線去松本 上高地（河童橋、大正池、田代池）上高地住宿<br />\n<br />\nDay 2 上高地經信濃大町上立山 落山後去宇奈月溫泉住宿 <br />\n<br />\nDay 3 黑部峽谷鐵道 去金澤 金澤住宿<br />\n<br />\nDay 4 金澤去五箇山，白川鄉 去高山平湯溫泉住<br />\n（有啲想去睇莊川櫻）<br />\n<br />\nDay 5 高山市行 搭4個鐘巴士晏就到河口湖睇芝櫻 返東京<br />\n<br />\n想問以上咁樣順唔順路？ 想買昇龍道3日券但係上網啲人又話去到full曬又盛，我仲要係黃金周，有冇巴打用過？ <br />\n另外我其實有差唔多10日假，想去埋名古屋，但係返東京坐新幹線又貴，巴士又要7個鐘，諗緊好唔好唔睇芝櫻去名古屋<br />\n<br />\n第一次自己去旅行，想認真plan返個好好睇睇既旅程？ 大家有咩意見？"},{"pid":"e2d69233f8797d12d1930fd2757fe1e7d571e2d3","tid":208411,"uid":34692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T14:04:34.000Z","msg":"真心好唔順路"},{"pid":"b6c64c5cb159ff1baf7f51a5539062456b43da86","tid":208411,"uid":34692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T14:08:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>4月29至 5月3<br />\n<br />\nDay 1 東京晨早搭新幹線去松本 上高地（河童橋、大正池、田代池）上高地住宿<br />\n<br />\nDay 2 上高地經信濃大町上立山 落山後去宇奈月溫泉住宿 <br />\n<br />\nDay 3 黑部峽谷鐵道 去金澤 金澤住宿<br />\n<br />\nDay 4 金澤去五箇山，白川鄉 去高山平湯溫泉住<br />\n（有啲想去睇莊川櫻）<br />\n<br />\nDay 5 高山市行 搭4個鐘巴士晏就到河口湖睇芝櫻 返東京<br />\n<br />\n想問以上咁樣順唔順路？ 想買昇龍道3日券但係上網啲人又話去到full曬又盛，我仲要係黃金周，有冇巴打用過？ <br />\n另外我其實有差唔多10日假，想去埋名古屋，但係返東京坐新幹線又貴，巴士又要7個鐘，諗緊好唔好唔睇芝櫻去名古屋<br />\n<br />\n第一次自己去旅行，想認真plan返個好好睇睇既旅程？ 大家有咩意見？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nday1 東京去河口湖 夜晚瞓松本<br />\nday2 松本去上高地 夜晚瞓白湯溫泉<br />\nday3 高山 夜晚瞓高山<br />\nday4 白川鄉五箇山 夜晚瞓金澤<br />\nday5 金澤一日遊 夜晚瞓富山<br />\nday6 立山黑部 夜晚瞓松本<br />\nday7 松本落名古屋....."},{"pid":"56cb2a0fef751d18e23f16fc22de22e8638b9437","tid":208411,"uid":40171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T14:10:30.000Z","msg":"個行程唔多順，尤其上高地同平湯溫泉好近<br />\n<br />\nbtw 5日行晒 個人覺得好趕"},{"pid":"a4094685da0425aaaed43c9210589bc4127bdfec","tid":208411,"uid":31666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T14:26:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\nday1 東京去河口湖 夜晚瞓松本<br />\nday2 松本去上高地 夜晚瞓白湯溫泉<span style=\"color: red;\">或者乘鞍平原？因為我搵咗間旅館好想試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\nday3 高山 夜晚瞓高山<br />\n<br />\nday4 白川鄉五箇山 夜晚瞓金澤<br />\n<br />\nday5 金澤一日遊 夜晚瞓富山 <span style=\"color: red;\">去埋黑部鐵路，夜晚訓宇奈月得唔得？</span><br />\n<br />\nday6 立山黑部 夜晚瞓松本<span style=\"color: red;\">或者搭夜巴返東京</span><br />\n<br />\n（day7 松本落名古屋.....）</blockquote>"},{"pid":"a209585917027ae0608433f603f6aaf28e7092c2","tid":208411,"uid":34692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T14:38:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\nday1 東京去河口湖 夜晚瞓松本<br />\nday2 松本去上高地 夜晚瞓白湯溫泉<span style=\"color: red;\">或者乘鞍平原？因為我搵咗間旅館好想試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\nday3 高山 夜晚瞓高山<br />\n<br />\nday4 白川鄉五箇山 夜晚瞓金澤<br />\n<br />\nday5 金澤一日遊 夜晚瞓富山 <span style=\"color: red;\">去埋黑部鐵路，夜晚訓宇奈月得唔得？</span><br />\n<br />\nday6 立山黑部 夜晚瞓松本<span style=\"color: red;\">或者搭夜巴返東京</span><br />\n<br />\n（day7 松本落名古屋.....）</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n住乘鞍高原冇所謂， 反正都喺附近<br />\n如果想去宇奈月、 黑部峽谷，不如你再加多一日啦，反正你有十日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab910c2613afba46ae4b088b54410ec3e4c66258","tid":208411,"uid":31666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T16:48:33.000Z","msg":"新方案<br />\nDay 1 東京搭巴士去松本 松本住一晚<br />\n<br />\nDay 2 經信濃過立山 宇奈月溫泉住一晚<br />\n<br />\nDay 3 黑部鐵路 金澤<br />\n<br />\nDay 4 金澤行一日  夜晚高岡住<br />\n<br />\nDay 5 高岡搭巴士 五箇山 白川鄉 高山住<br />\n<br />\nDay 6 高山 高穗纜車 平湯溫泉住 <br />\n<br />\nDay 7 上高地 經松本返東京"},{"pid":"08363b669dd51bf026a8258688b8e777f65b8493","tid":208411,"uid":34692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T05:53:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新方案<br />\nDay 1 東京搭巴士去松本 松本住一晚<br />\n<br />\nDay 2 經信濃過立山 宇奈月溫泉住一晚<br />\n<br />\nDay 3 黑部鐵路 金澤<br />\n<br />\nDay 4 金澤行一日  夜晚高岡住<br />\n<br />\nDay 5 高岡搭巴士 五箇山 白川鄉 高山住<br />\n<br />\nDay 6 高山 高穗纜車 平湯溫泉住 <br />\n<br />\nDay 7 上高地 經松本返東京</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁樣好好多<br />\nbtw 你day4 住埋金沢都得啦， 搬少一晚酒店，金澤去高岡45分鐘車啫"},{"pid":"f4d723efe0e634e5197cb056499d42f62c111b33","tid":208411,"uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T05:56:53.000Z","msg":"巴打<br />\n我都係黃金周打算上立山黑部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"717b732be51824ca8068e390f6585873e0348f3a","tid":208411,"uid":5143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T06:20:52.000Z","msg":"巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nrecap<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我上年六月去<br />\nday 1: HK-&gt;名古屋<br />\nday 2: 名古屋-&gt;高山-&gt;白川鄉-&gt;stay 金澤<br />\nday 3: 金澤-&gt;stay 富山<br />\nday 4: 富山-&gt;stay 立山黑部<br />\nday 5: 立山黑部-&gt;松本-&gt;stay松本溫泉<br />\nday 6: 松本溫泉-&gt;上高地-&gt;松本-&gt;stay 名古屋<br />\nday 7: 名古屋-&gt;Outlet(土岐)-&gt;名古屋, stay 名古屋<br />\nday 8: 名古屋-&gt; HK"},{"pid":"772e94182023eea024d28ddce3a7b886e1654d2d","tid":208411,"uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T06:35:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nrecap<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我上年六月去<br />\nday 1: HK-&gt;名古屋<br />\nday 2: 名古屋-&gt;高山-&gt;白川鄉-&gt;stay 金澤<br />\nday 3: 金澤-&gt;stay 富山<br />\nday 4: 富山-&gt;stay 立山黑部<br />\nday 5: 立山黑部-&gt;松本-&gt;stay松本溫泉<br />\nday 6: 松本溫泉-&gt;上高地-&gt;松本-&gt;stay 名古屋<br />\nday 7: 名古屋-&gt;Outlet(土岐)-&gt;名古屋, stay 名古屋<br />\nday 8: 名古屋-&gt; HK</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我打算東京來回<br />\n一日其實係咪太少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d34381780e17842788a4d322bbd0ab7c2ebfc378","tid":208411,"uid":31666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T06:40:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打<br />\n我都係黃金周打算上立山黑部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你係想一日去完立山返東京？ 我見yosoko有plan，你可以睇睇，順便一問，你住東京都邊度"},{"pid":"9a2667d538db259b754879669c489ef0596f2c5e","tid":208411,"uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T06:54:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打<br />\n我都係黃金周打算上立山黑部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你係想一日去完立山返東京？ 我見yosoko有plan，你可以睇睇，順便一問，你住東京都邊度</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係呀<br />\n其實如果上面有得留宿我都可以留既<br />\n我淨係打算買一set車飛去到搭<br />\n好似話去到2/3回程需時7-8 hrs only<br />\n本來諗住東京去大阪出然後番香港<br />\n但無奈單程機票太貴...都係東京番算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我book左bnb呀唔記得左係邊lu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41cba5a91ad7deb8db980237e6c5a23eefe847eb","tid":208411,"uid":31666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T09:46:19.000Z","msg":"上高地一日行唔行得曬？"},{"pid":"33de833aef2e577b1eb9f29f9ace8a388379f4b1","tid":208411,"uid":48277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T09:51:40.000Z","msg":"玩立山黑部就唔好玩黑部峽谷啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb4cdb2a509d93534697dff8e4961db641cab84a","tid":208411,"uid":31666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T09:52:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>玩立山黑部就唔好玩黑部峽谷啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解？"},{"pid":"fd857f278e933fb0a33a396b3607cc35fbab482c","tid":208411,"uid":41308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T09:53:02.000Z","msg":"日本人加强国人齊齊進攻<br />\n<br />\n祝你好運"},{"pid":"96391ef0f55a4bbdd082975b9a976f5cb0464052","tid":208411,"uid":31666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T09:55:43.000Z","msg":"真。究極方案<br />\n<br />\nDay 1 東京搭巴士去松本 松本住一晚<br />\n<br />\nDay 2 經信濃過立山 宇奈月溫泉住一晚<br />\n<br />\nDay 3 黑部鐵路 金澤<br />\n<br />\nDay 4 金澤行一日 夜晚金澤<br />\n<br />\nDay 5 高岡搭巴士 五箇山 白川鄉 高山住<br />\n<br />\nDay 6 高山 高穗纜車 平湯溫泉住 <br />\n<br />\nDay 7 上高地 上高住<br />\n<br />\nDay 8 返東京"},{"pid":"061e6c312c898b9dd611537eb16ffb27f1550bc2","tid":208411,"uid":48277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T09:56:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>玩立山黑部就唔好玩黑部峽谷啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解？</blockquote><br />\n唔順路到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己google下"},{"pid":"18e3b55de0a617d3a97daddf4a7e1f26f1b541e9","tid":208411,"uid":48277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T09:57:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真。究極方案<br />\n<br />\nDay 1 東京搭巴士去松本 松本住一晚<br />\n<br />\nDay 2 經信濃過立山 宇奈月溫泉住一晚<br />\n<br />\nDay 3 黑部鐵路 金澤<br />\n<br />\nDay 4 金澤行一日 夜晚金澤<br />\n<br />\nDay 5 高岡搭巴士 五箇山 白川鄉 高山住<br />\n<br />\nDay 6 高山 高穗纜車 平湯溫泉住 <br />\n<br />\nDay 7 上高地 上高住<br />\n<br />\nDay 8 返東京</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nday 2一定要住富山 你落山都天黑"},{"pid":"1d457a745d1880c6075f17a7217c7fd90642570d","tid":208411,"uid":5143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T10:03:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>玩立山黑部就唔好玩黑部峽谷啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解？</blockquote><br />\n唔順路到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己google下</blockquote><br />\n兩個地方隔超遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89b654dd3de4abc12f50c98817ee2b89fedc357e","tid":208411,"uid":66202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T10:29:53.000Z","msg":"你準備好交通住宿未? gw會好爆, 食方面都祝你好運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}